  "text": "A previous study using a lethal mouse-adapted, seasonal H3N2 influenza virus also found that TLR3 2/2 mice had improved survival (Le [CITATION_1] . It may be possible that the mouse-adapted lethal H3N2 virus model is more akin to our (non-mouse-adapted) H5N1 infection of mice. TLR3",
